data.description: Open house Monday 11/13/23 from 1-130 PM | 157 Curry Ave is a gorgeous property that sits on a quiet street in Turtle Creek, PA. This home has incredible value add features including, TWO CAR INTEGRAL GARAGE, CENTRAL AC, a NEWER FURNACE, and gorgeous HARDWOOD FLOORS THROUGHOUT. The bedrooms are spacious with plenty of room for storage and the kitchen CABINETS AND COUNTERTOPS ARE IN GREAT SHAPE! Being less than 30 minutes from Downtown Pittsburgh, and easy access to major roadway 376, makes this the PERFECT opportunity for end buyers and long-term tenants alike!
